      <title>印度法院下令各邦与干旱首都共享水资源</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/indian-court-orders-states-to-share-water-with-parched-capital</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度最高法院周四下令邻近各州增加对首都的供水，以帮助缓解因持续热浪造成的严重缺水现象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/indian-court-orders-states-to-share-water-with-parched-capital</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 13:05:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登政府寻求华尔街如何使用人工智能的意见</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/biden-administration-seeks-input-on-how-wall-street-is-using-ai</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国财政部正在寻求更多有关金融公司如何使用人工智能以及该技术给该行业带来的机遇和风险的信息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/biden-administration-seeks-input-on-how-wall-street-is-using-ai</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非工会敦促非国大考虑与民主联盟达成独立协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/south-african-elections-unions-suggest-anc-da-government-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位知情人士透露，南非最大的工会联合会正在敦促执政党非洲人国民大会考虑寻求主要反对党的支持，以使其在失去议会多数席位后继续执政。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/south-african-elections-unions-suggest-anc-da-government-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 12:52:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国承诺实施重大改革，重塑国家医疗体系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/china-pledges-key-reforms-to-revamp-nation-s-medical-system</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国国务院周四宣布了改革国家医疗体系的计划，承诺在从公立医院到保险支付等领域进行改革。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/china-pledges-key-reforms-to-revamp-nation-s-medical-system</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 12:47:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国公民因涉嫌间谍活动在俄罗斯被拘留</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/french-citizen-detained-in-russia-on-allegations-of-spying</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯当局称，他们拘留了一名法国公民，罪名是涉嫌从事间谍活动，这是自克里姆林宫发动乌克兰战争以来，俄罗斯逮捕了几名外国人的最新一次。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/french-citizen-detained-in-russia-on-allegations-of-spying</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 12:30:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>工会称卢旺达向人权法院提供政策建议不合法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/rwanda-policy-advice-on-human-rights-court-unlawful-union-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在针对英国政府备受争议的移民政策的最新挑战中，律师们辩称，英国大臣推翻欧洲人权法院裁决并将寻求庇护者送往卢旺达的命令是违法的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/rwanda-policy-advice-on-human-rights-court-unlawful-union-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 11:58:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>彭博经济分析显示，莫迪在政治分歧更严重的州惨败</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/modi-lost-big-in-states-where-divisive-politics-was-worse-be</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博经济研究分析显示，印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪在其政党政策失误和利用分裂政治赢得支持的邦份遭遇了其任期内最大的选举失败。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/modi-lost-big-in-states-where-divisive-politics-was-worse-be</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 11:55:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度出口民调引发批评、眼泪和调查呼吁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/india-s-exit-polls-were-wrong-prompting-criticism-apologies-investigations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度出口民调结果严重失准，预测总理纳伦德拉·莫迪领导的政党将在选举中取得压倒性胜利，此举引发民调公司本周公开道歉，并呼吁对可能存在的操纵行为进行调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/india-s-exit-polls-were-wrong-prompting-criticism-apologies-investigations</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 10:35:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>不了解拜登命令的移民在加州面临新规定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/migrants-unaware-of-biden-order-keep-streaming-into-san-diego</link>
      <description><![CDATA[星期三凌晨，42 岁的圣地亚哥·蒙特内格罗翻越了圣地亚哥南部 30 英尺高的边境墙，抵达了一个露天拘留所，离开祖国哥伦比亚后经历了漫长的旅程，他又冷又饿，又疲惫不堪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/migrants-unaware-of-biden-order-keep-streaming-into-san-diego</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 22:38:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
